.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啲汽水有陣奇怪味，唔知係無乜氣定點，係咪間間都係咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加水係常識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪加水我唔清楚 <br />\n不過可樂公司拎成個滅火筒嘅野去裝<br />\n啲氣同可樂好似係兩個筒嚟<br />\n如果冇乜氣可能部可樂機冇駁落/用曬冇fill翻啲氣落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申做過新鋪 個經理差唔多教曬啲野俾我哋識<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9711783290c2d67700484ca76e64ead12db60e83","tid":8433,"uid":38675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"再講<br />\n有三文魚嘅記住唔好吃<br />\n舊鋪嗰啲會擺左成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有陣時有啲著西裝嘅日本佬<br />\n其實佢哋就係香港薩利亞啲高層嚟<br />\n見到佢哋啲話 嗰日啲食物一定好企理<br />\n<br />\n話時話上次日本佬讚我卡哇依 代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0537ff55cf51ddcb541e4a416fefc2bb5ca94af","tid":8433,"uid":16408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再講<br />\n有三文魚嘅記住唔好吃<br />\n舊鋪嗰啲會擺左成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有陣時有啲著西裝嘅日本佬<br />\n其實佢哋就係香港薩利亞啲高層嚟<br />\n見到佢哋啲話 嗰日啲食物一定好企理<br />\n<br />\n話時話上次日本佬讚我卡哇依 代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}